\@doanenote {6}
macro:->Periodically
poled
lithium
niobate
(PPLN)
is
a
lithium
niobate
crystal
that
switches
polarity
in
a
periodic
fashion
and
is
used
for
achieving
quasi-phase-matching
in
nonlinear
optics.
\@endanenote 
